# Demo Builder — Orschell Excavating E-Commerce Full-Stack

## Status: COMPLETE

---

## What Was Built

### Backend (Surface — Node.js 22 + TypeScript + node:sqlite)

Service running at `http://127.0.0.1:3742` — confirmed LISTENING.

Files built in `data/runner-workspace/orschell-ecommerce/` on the Surface:
- `src/index.ts` — Express server, PORT 3742, CORS for michaelwegter.com + localhost
- `src/db/database.ts` — DatabaseSync schema + full seed (2 users, 5 categories, 25 products, 7 indexes, 2 demo orders)
- `src/middleware/auth.ts` — JWT auth (ORSCHELL_JWT_SECRET), requireAuth + requireAdmin
- `src/routes/auth.ts` — POST /auth/register, POST /auth/login, GET /auth/me
- `src/routes/products.ts` — GET /products (paginated, filterable), GET /products/:slug, POST/PUT/DELETE /products (admin)
- `src/routes/categories.ts` — GET /categories
- `src/routes/cart.ts` — GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /cart, /cart/items
- `src/routes/orders.ts` — POST /orders (atomic inventory decrement), GET /orders, GET /orders/:id
- `src/routes/admin.ts` — GET /admin/stats, GET/PUT /admin/inventory/:pid, GET /admin/orders, PUT /admin/orders/:id/status
- `src/types/index.ts` — TypeScript interfaces

`npm install` completed, `tsc` compiled to `dist/` — no errors.
Service registered in `data/services.json` as `orschell-ecommerce-api`, `run-server.ps1` owns it.

**22 REST endpoints total** — all documented in plan.

### Bridge Blueprint

`mw-backend/orschell_ecommerce_blueprint.py` — proxies `/demos/orschell-excavating-e-commerce-full/api/*` to `http://127.0.0.1:3742`. `accept-encoding` stripped to prevent gzip mismatch. Registered in `server.py` (NOT yet pushed — deploy step handles this).

### Frontend (React 18 + Vite + TypeScript)

Built and copied to `michaelwegter.com/public/demos/orschell-excavating-e-commerce-full/`. Base path `/demos/orschell-excavating-e-commerce-full/`. HashRouter for GH Pages SPA routing.

Source files (`upwork-runs/orschell-excavating-e-commerce-full/demo-src/src/`):
- `api/client.ts` — axios instance with JWT interceptor + typed helpers for all API endpoints
- `contexts/AuthContext.tsx` — JWT auth state, login/register/logout
- `contexts/CartContext.tsx` — cart state, drawer toggle, add/update/remove/clear
- `components/Navbar.tsx` — sticky, cart badge, user dropdown, admin link (conditional)
- `components/ProductCard.tsx` — image, category badge, price, add-to-cart, stock badges
- `components/CartDrawer.tsx` — slide-in drawer, quantity controls, checkout link
- `pages/Home.tsx` — hero banner, category grid, featured products
- `pages/Shop.tsx` — paginated grid, category sidebar filter, search
- `pages/ProductDetail.tsx` — image, breadcrumb, stock status, qty picker, add-to-cart
- `pages/Login.tsx` — login/register tabs, demo credential hints
- `pages/Checkout.tsx` — shipping form, mock payment form (labeled), order summary sidebar
- `pages/OrderConfirmation.tsx` — success state, items, payment ref
- `pages/Account.tsx` — profile + full order history with status badges
- `pages/Orders.tsx` — order detail with 4-step status pipeline visualization
- `pages/Admin.tsx` — 4-panel admin CMS: Dashboard (revenue chart + stats + recent orders), Products (CRUD), Inventory (inline edit), Orders (status pipeline + filter)

Vite build: 899 modules, ~637KB JS (recharts included). No errors.

### workSamples.js
Entry added: id 18, slug `orschell-excavating-e-commerce-full`, icon 🏗, color #F76B10, frameStyle walnut.

