## Design

Dark industrial theme: `#1C1F24` base, `#F76B10` orange accent, `#FFD600` yellow. Barlow Condensed (headings, uppercase) + Inter (body). Hazard-stripe dividers, 2px card borders with orange hover, uppercase badge pills.

